-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. A typical one.

You can see an open fridge. What a letdown! The fridge is empty! Look out! It's a- oh, never mind, it's just an oven. As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a table. There is an open frosted-glass door leading west. There is an exit to the east. You need an exit without a door? You should try going south.
